investigation.title: Plant Gravity Perception: Pilot (PGP Pilot)
investigation.description: This study examined tissue-specific early transcriptional responses upon reorientation in wild type and starchless pgm-1 mutant seedlings of Arabidopsis. Seedlings were grown in vertical Petri dishes for four days.

project.title: Characterizing Plant Gravity Perception Systems
project.funding: 201Space Biology Flight (ILSRA) NNH14ZTT002N , Grant/Contract No.: NNX15AG55G
